271
00:11:29.380 --> 00:11:31.380
I understand you're angry, but come back.

272
00:11:31.380 --> 00:11:32.380
Let's talk about it calmly.

273
00:11:32.380 --> 00:11:34.380
No, I've talked enough already,

274
00:11:34.380 --> 00:11:35.380
and nothing's changed.

275
00:11:35.380 --> 00:11:37.380
I'm never coming back!

276
00:11:37.380 --> 00:11:43.380
Was that Adelaide?

277
00:11:43.380 --> 00:11:48.380
She took the elevator.

278
00:11:57.380 --> 00:11:59.380
Now, forgive my intrusion.

279
00:11:59.380 --> 00:12:00.380
I couldn't help but sense

280
00:12:00.380 --> 00:12:02.380
some kind of frustration in you.

281
00:12:02.380 --> 00:12:04.380
Do you feel guilty that you couldn't help the girl?

282
00:12:04.380 --> 00:12:07.380
No! Get out of my head!

283
00:12:07.380 --> 00:12:09.380
You're trying to use my emotions to manipulate me,

284
00:12:09.380 --> 00:12:11.380
but I'll never help you hurt people!

285
00:12:11.380 --> 00:12:13.380
I understand your reaction.

286
00:12:13.380 --> 00:12:16.380
There are many misunderstandings about me.

287
00:12:16.380 --> 00:12:18.380
Unlike what you'd want to believe,

288
00:12:18.380 --> 00:12:21.380
I'm trying to help people, not hurt them.

289
00:12:21.380 --> 00:12:23.380
Wouldn't you desire a magical solution

290
00:12:23.380 --> 00:12:25.380
that could heal people, for example?

291
00:12:25.380 --> 00:12:28.380
There is no such thing as a magical solution.

292
00:12:28.380 --> 00:12:30.380
And yet that's what Ladybug does, doesn't she?

293
00:12:30.380 --> 00:12:33.380
Magically fixing everything with a swing of her yo-yo?

294
00:12:33.380 --> 00:12:35.380
Thanks to me, you could do the same

295
00:12:35.380 --> 00:12:37.380
and put an end to people's needless suffering.

296
00:12:37.380 --> 00:12:40.380
I can sense your hesitation, and perhaps you're right.

297
00:12:40.380 --> 00:12:42.380
People should find their paths on their own.

298
00:12:42.380 --> 00:12:45.380
Who cares if they suffer for months, sometimes years on end?

299
00:12:45.380 --> 00:12:47.380
I'll leave you be.

300
00:12:47.380 --> 00:12:49.380
No, wait! I...

301
00:12:49.380 --> 00:12:51.380
I'll give it a try.

302
00:12:51.380 --> 00:12:54.380
You will? In that case, what should I call you?

303
00:12:54.380 --> 00:12:56.380
Reckless driver.

304
00:12:56.380 --> 00:13:04.380
Aglaya! Aglaya, what happened?

305
00:13:04.380 --> 00:13:06.380
This was never a good idea.

306
00:13:06.380 --> 00:13:08.380
I can't be healed.

307
00:13:08.380 --> 00:13:10.380
I'm going home and shutting myself away forever.

308
00:13:10.380 --> 00:13:12.380
There's nothing that can be done!

309
00:13:12.380 --> 00:13:14.380
The first session is an unexceptional experience

310
00:13:14.380 --> 00:13:16.380
in seven out of ten cases.

311
00:13:16.380 --> 00:13:18.380
It doesn't mean you should stop.

312
00:13:18.380 --> 00:13:22.380
Aglaya, come back!

313
00:13:22.380 --> 00:13:25.380
I can heal you instantly now, just like you wanted.

314
00:13:25.380 --> 00:13:28.380
No, you've been akumatized!

315
00:13:28.380 --> 00:13:31.380
What are you doing?

316
00:13:31.380 --> 00:13:33.380
I'm going to try to help Aglaya.

317
00:13:33.380 --> 00:13:35.380
I'll be super careful, I promise.

318
00:13:35.380 --> 00:13:42.380
I think it's best to cut Dr. Stika's session short for today.

319
00:13:42.380 --> 00:13:44.380
Tiki, spots on!

320
00:13:44.380 --> 00:13:51.380
Don't tell me you want to play Cat Noir and rescue your girlfriend.

321
00:13:51.380 --> 00:13:53.380
Precisely! Plagg Klauser!

322
00:13:53.380 --> 00:14:19.380
Quite significant.

323
00:14:19.380 --> 00:14:21.380
I know you have a phobia of insects,

324
00:14:21.380 --> 00:14:23.380
and more specifically of these awful butterflies,

325
00:14:23.380 --> 00:14:25.380
but I'll fix it for you.

326
00:14:25.380 --> 00:14:31.380
There, you are now demonized and free from all your fears.

327
00:14:31.380 --> 00:14:43.380
Thanks to Reckless Driver, I'm no longer scared of anything!

328
00:14:43.380 --> 00:14:47.380
Okay, still stay here, it's safer.

329
00:14:47.380 --> 00:14:50.380
There's no danger! She healed me! How amazing!

330
00:14:50.380 --> 00:14:53.380
Yeah, well, she still needs to be de-akumatized.

331
00:14:53.380 --> 00:14:57.380
You must, but it's a shame she's a great superhero too.

332
00:14:57.380 --> 00:15:10.380
I'm on the akumatized villain's track, m'lady.

333
00:15:17.380 --> 00:15:20.380
Two safety measures are better than one.

334
00:15:20.380 --> 00:15:22.380
No need for safety, Cat Noir.

335
00:15:22.380 --> 00:15:25.380
I used to be afraid of cars, but not anymore.

336
00:15:25.380 --> 00:15:27.380
You can't stay here, sir.

337
00:15:27.380 --> 00:15:30.380
Why not? This is where the sun is.

338
00:15:30.380 --> 00:15:32.380
True, but it's also where cars are.

339
00:15:32.380 --> 00:15:36.380
That's okay. Drivers have eyes. They'll avoid me.

340
00:15:36.380 --> 00:15:40.380
I'm sorry, but I can't let you take this kind of risk.

341
00:15:45.380 --> 00:15:47.380
Hey, team. Blast!

342
00:15:47.380 --> 00:15:52.380
Clash!

343
00:15:52.380 --> 00:16:06.380
Are you afraid of me, Ladybug? Quite significant.

344
00:16:06.380 --> 00:16:09.380
Of course I'm not. We just have to stop you.

345
00:16:09.380 --> 00:16:11.380
But you're not sure whether it's the right thing to do.

346
00:16:11.380 --> 00:16:15.380
I am. You can't speed up solutions like this without there being some other price to pay.

347
00:16:15.380 --> 00:16:17.380
Sometimes meaningful help takes time.

348
00:16:17.380 --> 00:16:19.380
Are you sure?

349
00:16:19.380 --> 00:16:31.380
She's going to drive us buggered.

350
00:16:31.380 --> 00:16:35.380
That's quite a significant observation. We could go for some group therapy.

351
00:16:35.380 --> 00:16:38.380
I'd rather go for a...

352
00:16:38.380 --> 00:16:41.380
Lucky charm!

353
00:16:41.380 --> 00:16:48.380
Uh, okay. Not sure this will help.

354
00:16:48.380 --> 00:16:53.380
What in the world is all this?

355
00:16:53.380 --> 00:17:05.380
Those are some awesome illusions, Rena.

356
00:17:09.380 --> 00:17:11.380
Pegasus, we need your portals.

357
00:17:11.380 --> 00:17:13.380
Voyage!

358
00:17:13.380 --> 00:17:18.380
Looks like it's bad time.

359
00:17:18.380 --> 00:17:24.380
The ultracromer must be in the car, kitty cat.

360
00:17:24.380 --> 00:17:27.380
We'll try, milady. Cataclysm!

361
00:17:27.380 --> 00:17:31.380
Cano R, everything okay?

362
00:17:31.380 --> 00:17:34.380
Let's see what you're afraid of, cat.

363
00:17:36.380 --> 00:17:40.380
Oh, of course, revealing your secret identity. Quite significant.

364
00:17:40.380 --> 00:17:43.380
Well, time to de-evilize.

365
00:17:43.380 --> 00:17:48.380
There, you are now de-evilized and free.

366
00:17:48.380 --> 00:17:49.380
What's going on?

367
00:17:49.380 --> 00:17:52.380
It's fine, reckless driver. I'm just helping you.

368
00:17:52.380 --> 00:17:59.380
I've deprived him of his powers. He is at your mercy. You can see he's as miraculous now.

369
00:17:59.380 --> 00:18:02.380
That's not significant at all. I told you I only want to do good.

370
00:18:02.380 --> 00:18:07.380
Precisely. If we got our hands on the cat miraculous, we'd only need the ladybug one.

371
00:18:07.380 --> 00:18:11.380
Then we can make a wish for people to be freed from their fears all across the world.

372
00:18:11.380 --> 00:18:14.380
That would be very significant, wouldn't it?

373
00:18:14.380 --> 00:18:21.380
Milady, am I glad to see you. This akumatized villain is amazing.

374
00:18:21.380 --> 00:18:25.380
Thanks to her, I no longer am afraid of revealing my secret identity. I can finally tell you.

375
00:18:25.380 --> 00:18:28.380
No talking with your mouth full, kitty cat.

376
00:18:32.380 --> 00:18:33.380
Turn!

377
00:18:33.380 --> 00:18:39.380
Holy mouse!

378
00:18:39.380 --> 00:18:41.380
Attack!

379
00:18:41.380 --> 00:18:59.380
Whenever you're ready, purple tigress.

380
00:18:59.380 --> 00:19:00.380
Clutch!

381
00:19:03.380 --> 00:19:04.380
Clutch!

382
00:19:04.380 --> 00:19:10.380
Why hasn't she transformed back?

383
00:19:10.380 --> 00:19:13.380
I don't see an ultracuma, which means it wasn't in the car.

384
00:19:13.380 --> 00:19:17.380
Maybe it was something inside the car.

385
00:19:17.380 --> 00:19:28.380
No more evil doing for you, ultracuma.

386
00:19:33.380 --> 00:19:35.380
Time to de-evilize!

387
00:19:35.380 --> 00:19:40.380
Gotcha!

388
00:19:40.380 --> 00:19:43.380
Bye-bye, little butterfly.

389
00:19:43.380 --> 00:19:45.380
I mean...

390
00:19:45.380 --> 00:19:47.380
Miraculous ladybug!

391
00:20:00.380 --> 00:20:04.380
This magical charm will help you remember that you should believe in yourself.

392
00:20:04.380 --> 00:20:07.380
You're a good therapist. I'm sure you've helped a lot of people.

393
00:20:07.380 --> 00:20:12.380
People who've had family problems, phobias, or communication issues.

394
00:20:12.380 --> 00:20:16.380
You never needed a magical solution because you already know how to de-evilize people.

395
00:20:16.380 --> 00:20:17.380
For good.

396
00:20:17.380 --> 00:20:20.380
Even though it can take a while sometimes.

397
00:20:20.380 --> 00:20:22.380
Thank you, ladybug.

398
00:20:22.380 --> 00:20:24.380
Hound it!

399
00:20:24.380 --> 00:20:28.380
You will tell me your secret in the end, ladybug.

400
00:20:28.380 --> 00:20:31.380
And when you do, it won't be the way you think.

401
00:20:31.380 --> 00:20:35.380
I'm sorry. It's my fault you got akumatized.

402
00:20:35.380 --> 00:20:39.380
No, it's not. I let my own emotions get the better of me.

403
00:20:39.380 --> 00:20:41.380
Besides, it's over now.

404
00:20:41.380 --> 00:20:42.380
But I'm still afraid.

405
00:20:42.380 --> 00:20:47.380
Fear can be a good thing. It teaches us to be cautious and not put ourselves in danger.

406
00:20:47.380 --> 00:20:52.380
But in your case, fear of insects has become a phobia that keeps you from enjoying your life.

407
00:20:52.380 --> 00:20:56.380
That's why we're here with your friends to help you feel better.

408
00:20:57.380 --> 00:21:01.380
Go as far as you want and stop anytime you want, okay?

409
00:21:26.380 --> 00:21:28.380
Do you want to go back out?

410
00:21:28.380 --> 00:21:30.380
Yes.

411
00:21:30.380 --> 00:21:34.380
That's an excellent start, Aglaie.

412
00:21:34.380 --> 00:21:39.380
And now you know no matter how long it takes, you won't be alone to travel your path.

413
00:21:39.380 --> 00:21:41.380
You've found a wonderful vehicle.

414
00:21:41.380 --> 00:21:42.380
Friendship.

415
00:21:42.380 --> 00:21:55.380
Thanks for coming with me and for understanding my need to talk to Dr. Sika.

416
00:21:55.380 --> 00:21:56.380
Of course.

417
00:21:56.380 --> 00:21:57.380
Adrian Agrest?

418
00:21:57.380 --> 00:22:09.380
So what do you need to talk about, Adrian?

419
00:22:09.380 --> 00:22:14.380
There's something strange about my father.